    "title": "Genesis AI Image Design System (指哪生哪图) Architecture",
    "summary": "Comprehensive overview of the Genesis AI Image Design System (Briefing Studio). Key technical features include robust React state management (solving async stale closures and state overwrites), and high-performance browser-native DOCX image extraction utilizing FileReader and manual Buffer polyfills for Mammoth.js compatibility. The AI generation pipeline implements strict structural constraints through dimension-aware prompts and imageCount synchronization to ensure aesthetic stability. Reliability is enhanced by removing client-side timeouts for complex LLM tasks and implementing distinctive schema descriptions to prevent content duplication across multiple text blocks. UI refinements include self-correcting auto-font-sizing that preserves manual user adjustments and a full-canvas blurry loading mask during generation.",
